---
title: Vietnamese-Style Pork & Peanuts with Garlic Rice, Sesame Veggies & Fried Egg
description: Whisk away your taste buds to the beautiful land of Vietnam with this rice bowl recipe! Juicy pork mince gets a hit of ginger and
hoisin sauce, before being piled on top of aromatic garlic rice and sautéed veggies for an unbeatable simple-yet-elegant meal that’s wonderfully addictive, light and tasty.
